Value: Canterbury Resources Limited explores for mineral properties in Australia and Papua New Guinea. The company primarily explores for copper, molybdenum, and gold deposits. Its property portfolio includes 100% owned Briggs, Mannersley, and Fig Tree tenements located in Queensland; and Ekuti Range, Wamum, and Bismarck projects located in Papua New Guinea. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Pyrmont, Australia.
